full_desc: ADCID must match the ADCID of the center uploading the data
Only one Initial Visit Packet (PACKET="I", "IF", "IL") and Initial UDSv4 Visit Packet (PACKET="I4) is allowed per participant
Cannot find a matching UDS visit packet with the same visit number and visit date as the module packet
Follow-Up module packet (PACKET="FF" or "FL") cannot be submitted for a UDS Initial Visit Packet (PACKET="I")
Participant must have an approved UDS, BDS, or MDS packet before a Milestone form can be submitted
Two packets cannot have the same visit number (VISITNUM) if they are from different dates (VISITDATE)
Two packets cannot have the same visit date (VISITDATE) if they are from different visit numbers (VISITNUM)
Follow-Up Visit Packet (PACKET="F", "FF", "FL") visit date (VISITDATE) cannot be equal to or from a date before the respective Initial Visit Packet (PACKET="I", "I4", "IF", "IL")
Visit date (VISITDATE) for UDSv4 Initial Visit Packet (PACKET=I4) must be a date after the last UDSv3 Visit Packet
Following fields in the input record do not match with the submitted version/packet of the form/module: [list of field names]
Provided PACKET code is not in the list of accepted packets for this module
Provided FORMVER is not in the list of accepted versions for this module
PTID must be no more than 10 characters
MODULE is not in list of accepted modules
Follow-Up visit cannot be submitted without an existing Initial Visit Packet
More than one IVP packet found for the participant/module
UDS visit packet must be approved before the module visit can be processed
To submit an Initial UDSv4 Visit Packet (PACKET="I4"), participant must have an existing UDSv3 Visit Packet
Participant must have an existing Initial UDSv4 Visit Packet (PACKET="I4") submitted before the Follow-Up Visit Packet (PACKET="F")
Duplicate record with the same visit date exists in the batch CSV file for this participant
Missing submission status (MODE<form name>) variables for one or more optional forms
Participant must have an approved UDS, BDS, or MDS packet before the NP form can be submitted
DECEASED and AUTOPSY should both equal 1 in the most recent Milestone form in order for the NP form to be accepted
Date of death of the most recent Milestone form (DEATHMO, DEATHDY, DEATHYR) must match the date of death on the on NP form (NPDODMO, NPDODDY, NPDODYR)
The date of death on the on the NP form (NPDODMO, NPDODDY, NPDODYR) cannot be a date before the last UDS visit date (VISITDATE) for the participant
Sex reported on the NP form (NPSEX) does not match with the sex/birthsex reported on the UDS initial visit packet
Age at death (NPDAGE) reported on the NP form does not match with the value computed from the date of death on the NP form and the participant date of birth reported on the UDS initial visit packet
A UDS packet must be submitted before submitting this module/form
